'''Wet Droids''' was a derogatory term that was used to refer to [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] or [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commandos]]. The phrase was originally coined by the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] [[Sergeant/Legends|Sergeant]] [[Kal Skirata]].

==Appearances==
